text: Hameed () is a village in the Chach Valley of Hazro Tehsil in Attock District of Punjab Province, Pakistan. Hameed is located in western Chhachh,Chach (Chhachch) - Imperial Gazetteer of India, v. 10, p. 115 about 4 km from the city of Hazro.Gazetteer of the Rawalpindi district 1893-94 published by Sang- E-Meel Publications and Page 259 Hameed has its own union council, which also governs other surrounding villages. ==References== Category:Populated places in Attock District Category:Regions of Pakistan
